    """Encodes text into tokens, tracking the starting character position of each token.

    Special tokens are matched as whole units (position = start of the special token text);
    ordinary text is split using `pat_str` and BPE-encoded piece by piece, with each
    resulting token's position derived from its byte offset within the piece.
    """
